          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "主料：香葱500g，大葱500g，紫葱头500g，切面（细）5kg;",
          "block_bbox": [
            89,
            576,
            602,
            637
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "辅料：水300g，油菜500g，食用油500g；",
          "block_bbox": [
            88,
            650,
            518,
            676
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "调料：酱油1kg。",
          "block_bbox": [
            89,
            688,
            257,
            712
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "制作过程",
          "block_bbox": [
            91,
            742,
            199,
            770
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "香葱切段，大葱、葱头切丝，油菜切开备用；葱油制作：锅内放油烧至三成热，将香葱、大葱、葱头入锅小火熬制20分钟后加酱油、水，开锅10分钟盛出；锅中煮面条的同时放一个小油菜，煮熟后浇上葱油、撒上香葱粒即可（原料按35碗计算）。",
          "block_bbox": [
            90,
            787,
            602,
            957
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "工艺技巧",
          "block_bbox": [
            99,
            987,
            203,
            1013
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "面条要细；熬油温度不宜太高。",
          "block_bbox": [
            142,
            1031,
            436,
            1053
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "品质特点",
          "block_bbox": [
            101,
            1081,
            206,
            1108
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 10
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
